---
tags: [ personal, object storage ]
---
# To issue commands:
linode-cli <command> <action>

# To create a bucket:
linode-cli obj mb <bucket>

# To remove a bucket:
linode-cli obj rb <bucket>

# To upload a public object:
linode-cli obj put --acl-public <object> <bucket>

# To download an object:
linode-cli obj get <bucket> <object>

# To remove an object:
linode-cli obj rm <bucket> <object>

# To list all available buckets:
linode-cli obj ls

# To list all objects in a bucket:
linode-cli obj ls <bucket>

# To view object help:
linode-cli obj --help

# To update:
pip3 install linode-cli --upgrade

